proftpd, as provided with UCS 2.0 and higher, has been enhanced with 
kerberos support using mod_gss.

To activate kerberos support for proftpd, add the following line to
/etc/proftpd/modules.conf:

LoadModule mod_gss.c

/etc/proftpd/proftpd.conf has to be adjusted accordingly. See
http://gssmod.sourceforge.net/ for details.


